OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe specific cuts to programmes are
OL,7,Finteresting.
OL,9,FDo I detect room for compromise and
OL,10,Fbacktracking?
OL,12,FA deal to save The World Tonight which
OL,13,Fwas recently the focus of industrial
OL,14,Faction over shifts? A way to keep a
OL,15,Ffull ` or at least substantial `
OL,16,FMidnight News?
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
