SC,0008
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FWe all know loyal Radio 4 listeners are
OL,7,Famongst the BBC's biggest supporters `
OL,8,Fand the most vocal critical friends if
OL,9,Fthey don't like something. I bet
OL,10,Fthey'll be writing to their MPs even
OL,11,Fnow.
OL,13,FCould this lead to cuts somewhere else?
OL,14,FR4 programmes saved while digital radio
OL,15,Fstations are cut?
OL,17,FOn TV, I'm sorry about Breakfast on
OL,18,FSunday though to be fair it suffers
OL,19,Ffrom being split between BBC One and
OL,20,FTwo.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15109
SC,0009
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FI tend to subscribe to the argument
OL,7,Fthat BBC Three and Four need to come to
OL,8,Fan end.
OL,10,FThe focus should be on the two showcase
OL,11,Fchannels and the iPlayer.
OL,13,FThere can be room for youth content on
OL,14,FBBC Two as long as it is clearly
OL,15,Fsignposted.
OL,17,FCould moving Newsnight on Fridays
OL,18,Fcreate an opportunity for a zone? Just
OL,19,Fdon't go back to the misguided BBC
OL,20,FThree zone on One at 10.35pm.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15110
SC,0010
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G10/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FSimilarly BBC Two should be home to the
OL,7,Fchallenging content lost to Four twenty
OL,8,Fyears ago. As long as the different
OL,9,Ffaces of the channel are properly
OL,10,Fsignposted, that can work.
OL,12,FI also tend to agree with the calls to
OL,13,Fcut daytime commissioning. There are
OL,14,Ftoo many "low end" bulk commissions.
OL,16,FFocus on those like Morning Live and
OL,17,FBargain Hunt which are popular or have
OL,18,Fimpact.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15111
SC,0011
