OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G11/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut I say this with regret as I'm all
OL,7,Ftoo aware of how important proper
OL,8,Fdaytime TV is to the elderly and
OL,9,Fhousebound.
OL,11,FOf course, there is no question of a
OL,12,Fblank screen but just as in 1975 and
OL,13,F1985, the elderly and housebound would
OL,14,Fbe the innocent ` and sometimes
OL,15,Fvoiceless ` victims of cuts. However
OL,16,Fthe alternative is worse for everyone.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15112
SC,0012
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G12/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FCutting jobs and cuts to the kind of
OL,7,Fprogrammes of quality or depth which
OL,8,Fothers may not make will not make the
OL,9,FBBC better for anyone. They are a
OL,10,Fresponse to an underlying situation
OL,11,Fwhich needs addressed urgently.
OL,13,FWhoever is PM in a few weeks time needs
OL,14,Fto address the challenges facing public
OL,15,Fservice broadcasting urgently.
OL,17,FAnd all of us who care about the BBC
OL,18,Fneed to get right behind the
OL,19,Forganisation and its staff. Not to
OL,20,Fmention managers facing unpalatable
OL,21,Fchoices too. They are not the bad guys.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15113
SC,0013
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1784144490
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}        G13/13
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC: a universal service
OL,4,Cthat's no longer universally paid for
OL,5,
OL,6,FNiggles about the things we don't like
OL,7,F` however legitimate ` should not be
OL,8,Fmistaken for fundamental hostility.
OL,9,FRather, they're a sign of underlying
OL,10,Fsupport and concern.
OL,12,FOne final thought.
OL,14,FIs some of the difficulty the BBC faces
OL,15,Fwith younger audiences now the result
OL,16,Fof misguided moves 20 years ago to
OL,17,Ffocus CBBC purely on those aged 12 and
OL,18,Funder? Older children and teenagers
OL,19,Fwere effectively abandoned in the
OL,20,Fprocess.
OL,23,EPub: 20-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
